creator: HGM Automotive Electronics, Inc.
descriptionHtml: This is the mobile setup app for HGM's COMPUSHIFT line of controllers. While connected to a controller, you can adjust shift and lockup points, view diagnostics, get information about your transmission, and much more. You can also save configurations, edit them with the controller off, and load them into the controller.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Improved appearance and performance of graph editors
Slightly improved performance of the Settings page
Fixed getting stuck attempting to save calibrations
